					<msContents>
						<summary><title>Book of Hours</title>. The manuscript contains texts in
							several languages: A Calendar of which November and December are
							missing,'Evangelium Secundum Iohannem', which is the 2nd
							Gospel according to St. John, some prayers and hymns of which pp. 231-50
							and pp. 333-38 are written in French. The pages 167-68 contain a prayer
							to the Virgin in Italian and on 3 inserted leaves from <date notBefore="1690" notAfter="1710">c. 1700</date> a description of the
							manuscript itself, written in Latin, is found.</summary>
						<msItem n="1" class="helgs malvg bibl salm ban texfr">
